node.text: Here’s to a community borne from mountains. Because, while seasons change, the mountains always endure. From big city or small, snowy town – we’re all skiers. And, when we stand together, we’re as tall as the mountains. #WeAreTheMTNS. 💚🏔💚 With gratitude for this amazing community, @IkonPass doubled renewal discounts for 20/21, and extended all savings until May 27. Together, we will endure.

OPERATIONS UPDATE: The mountain and on-mountain restaurants will be closed tomorrow, August 19. 

Deer Valley Grocery~Cafe will be open regular hours. 

We will be extending our Twilight Ride Series one more week. Join us on Tuesday, August 24 from 3 p.m. to 7 p.m. for the final Twilight Ride of the year. 

Trail conditions will be evaluated daily going forward as we have received a lot of rain in the last 24 hours.
